      "id": "PopularPost61847",
      "post_content": "Pretty much a tri-land. It sets you back a land, but it comes into play untapped...and, as the oracle says, you can tap it in response to sacrificing it. Thus, it could also be seen as a 1-time source for three mana. Not bad, I'd say. 4/5, at least, for me.",
